720161f-a.title: Manhattan: Greenwich Avenue - Horatio Street
720161f-a.text:
Greenwich Avenue, north fromm and including Horatio Street, to and
including Eighth Avenue (where it terminates). Also shown (background,
left) are Nos. 79 to 71 Eighth Avenue, at, adjoining and south of the
S.W. corner of West 14th Street. In the right background appear the
Jackson Square Branch of the New York Public Library, No. 251 Vest 13th
Street, and the Greenwich sub-station power plant of the city-owned
(Eighth Avenue) subway. In center background, is visible(in part) the
rectangularly shaped Port of l:ew York Authority Building, on the north
aide of West 15th Street from Eighth to 1inth Avenues.
